    <h2>What are "Business Decision Records"?</h2>
    <p>
      Business Decision Records (BDRs) are documents written to capture significant strategic decisions,
      in the style of software architecture decision records. We have found ADRs to be very useful to
      retrospect and introspect on our software projects. BDRs are an attempt to bring that utility to the
      arc of our business.
    </p>
